---
import MainLayout from "../layout/MainLayout.astro";

import Container from "../components/ui/Container.astro";

import Button from "../components/ui/Button.astro";
---

<MainLayout>
  <Container>
    <div class="max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-6xl
        md:text-8xl
        mb-8">
        About Through Indonesia
      </h1>

      <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-10">
        Discover Indonesia Through Local Eyes
      </p>

      <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-10">
        Photography expeditions and private journeys designed for photographers,
        storytellers, and adventurous travelers seeking authentic experiences
        across the Indonesian archipelago.
      </p>

      <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-10">
        From remote wilderness and extraordinary wildlife to vibrant cultures
        and breathtaking landscapes, each journey is thoughtfully crafted to
        reveal the true spirit of Indonesia through meaningful encounters,
        immersive experiences, and unforgettable photographic opportunities.
      </p>

      <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-10">
        Led by local experts with deep knowledge of Indonesia's people,
        traditions, and natural wonders, Through Indonesia offers more than a
        photography trip—it is an invitation to experience Indonesia from
        within.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Container>
</MainLayout>
